data: {"type": "response.reasoning_summary_text.done", "item_id": "item_e5999d763455", "output_index": 0, "summary_index": 0, "text": "The user wants me to use the `record_fact` tool exactly once with the value \"blue-cat\".\nI need to output the XML tool call first, then any prose (though the prompt says \"Do not answer in visible text\", implying the tool call is the main event, but I should follow the format).\nWait, the prompt says \"Do not answer in visible text\" which usually means the tool call is the only thing, or the tool call comes first.\nLet's construct the XML.\n\nTool: `record_fact`\nParameter: `value` = \"blue-cat\"\n\nOutput:\n<tool_call>\n<function=record_fact>\n<parameter=value>\nblue-cat\n</parameter>\n</function>\n</tool_call>\n", "sequence_number": 186}

